    <section id="projects" class="projCont">
      <div class="container1 top-pad1">
       <div class="heading3">
          <i class="far fa-address-card"></i>
          <span>INTRODUCTION</span>
        </div>
          <div class="contain">
            <p class="content">
                The programs of Sahyog involve intensive constant support 
                of the selected households to ensure that they have access to the basic necessities to 
                sustain livelihood which includes food, healthcare and free quality education. We focus 
                on implementing a community monitoring system to support and track the proper 
                functioning of  government educational institutions
            </p>
            <p class="content">
              We at Sahyog provides regular supply of ration kits and aiding healthcare for over 800 households 
              and look at implementation of quality healthcare through CHCs and PHCs
              We actively collaborate with the government and other organizations to drive change and impact 
              in education, healthcare and community development.
              With constant demand and with the use of RTI 20 new Anganwadis have started and about 800 for children 
              between 3 to 5 years, in addition pregnant mothers and adolescents also get benefits.
              For example, child supplementary nutrition, pre-primary education, special treatment for malnourished 
              children, health check-up for adolescents, supplementary nutrition, health check-up for pregnant mothers, vaccination, supplementary nutrition, etc.
            </p>
          </div>
        <hr color="#000000">
        <div class="all-items">
          <% for (i = 0; i < programs.length; i++) { %>
          <div class="item">
            <div class="left">
              <div class="img">
                <img src="<%= programs[i].main_image%>" alt="" class="pimg">
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="right">
              <h2 class="project-title"><%= programs[i].title%></h2>
              <p class="project-desc"><%= programs[i].description%></p>
              <div class="buttons">
                <a href="/programs/<%= programs[i]._id %>" class="primary-btn">Know More</a>
              </div>  
              <% if(currentUser){%>
                <a class="btn btn-warning" href="/programs/<%= programs[i]._id %>/edit/">Edit</a>
                <form class="delete-form" action="/programdelete/<%= programs[i]._id %>?_method=DELETE" method="POST">
                  <button class="btn btn-danger">DELETE</button>
                </form>
              <% } %>
            </div>
          </div>
          <% } %> 
          </div>
          <% if(currentUser){%>
            <center><a class="btn btn-success center5" href="/programnew">Add New Program</a></center>
          <% } %>
          <div class="item">
            <div class="left">
              <div class="img">
                <img src="images\1588341649033.jpg" alt="" class="pimg">
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="right">
              <h2 class="project-title">Covid-19 Response</h2>
              <p class="project-desc">Sahyog has managed to aid disadvantaged households through the provision of 
                rations over multiple cycles. Migrant workers who had 
                lost their jobs as a result of the pandemic were identified and transported across the country. </p>
              <div class="buttons">
                <a href="/covid" class="primary-btn">Know More</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

